

Official implementation of

"Deep Selective Encoder-Decoder Network for High-Density Salt-and-Pepper Noise Removal"

## Requirements

- Python 3.10
- TensorFlow 2.x
- NumPy
- OpenCV
- Matplotlib
#training
Run the files: 
python SPN.py
python datagenerator.py
python model.py
python train.py
weights automatically saved in weights folder

## Testing
python test.py



